sec.p:
In the fed-batch cultivation, feed was started after the initial glucose was consumed as indicated by a sharp increase in pO2. An exponential feed profile was used. For a desired specific growth rate μset (h−1), the volumetric feed rate Fglc (L h−1) was calculated from (Eq. 1) [13]: 1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
